# Local dev secrets for the Worker. Copy to `.dev.vars` (which is gitignored)
# and fill in. For PRODUCTION, set each with `wrangler secret put <NAME>` —
# `.dev.vars` is only read during `npm run dev` / local builds.

# Fine-grained GitHub PAT with "Issues: Read and write" on the target repo.
# Used by POST /api/park-request to open labelled `park-request` issues, which
# trigger .github/workflows/add-park.yml. Without it, /api/park-request is 503.
GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_xxxxxxxx

# Cloudflare Turnstile SECRET key (pairs with VITE_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY on the
# client). For local testing, Cloudflare's always-passes test secret works:
TURNSTILE_SECRET=1x0000000000000000000000000000000AA

# Optional: override the target repo. Defaults to marcialc/trailside-trivia.
# GITHUB_REPO=marcialc/trailside-trivia

# (existing) Cloudflare AI Gateway token used by the add-park pipeline.
# CF_AIG_TOKEN=...
